      <title>大胆猜测，淘汰失败</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/make-bold-guesses-and-weed-out-the-failures.zh/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 May 2021 16:33:22 +0000</pubDate>
